246
00:27:28,041 --> 00:27:30,166
TOKONG FENGYUAN
PANGLIMA ALTAR TENGAH

247
00:27:30,250 --> 00:27:31,583
Awak mungkin tak tahu,

248
00:27:32,416 --> 00:27:34,625
