- Ya.

341
00:36:22,333 --> 00:36:23,875
UNTUK RAMPAS HARTA PUSAKA,

342
00:36:23,958 --> 00:36:27,375
EN. LI GUNA HANTU BUNUH ORANG TUANYA,
DIA MAHU ELAK HUKUMAN

343
00:36:27,458 --> 00:36:28,875
BELASAH DIA

344
00:36:32,333 --> 00:36:33,541
Tunggu!

345
00:36:33,625 --> 00:36:35,541
Saya datang nak berunding.

346
00:36:35,625 --> 00:36:37,666
Bukankah awak patut tanya bos dulu?

347
00:36:42,750 --> 00:36:46,458
Saya tak perlu tanya.
Arahannya tak pernah berubah.

348
00:36:46,916 --> 00:36:47,750
